title: Willie Nelson - Live Country Music Concert (1966) [FLAC]
description:
downloaded from Qobuz

This is an interesting album chronicling an early show by Nelson. From time to time, the audience will shout song titles, and he actually talks between songs. While many people don't like live albums, this is actually more fun than some of his later live records. ~ Jim Worbois, Allmusic

01 Mr. Record Man / Hello Walls / One Day at a Time
02 The Last Letter / Half a Man
03 I Never Cared for You
04 Yesterday

09 Night Life

11 My Own Peculiar Way
